arcade.core.agent.cell

Interface CellFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PatchCellFactory, PottsCellFactory

    public interface CellFactory
    Factory class for Cell objects.

    The factory manages the creation of Cell objects by either:

    • Loading existing CellContainer instances from a given JSON file
    • Generating new CellContainer instances based on population settings
